<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>At the moment I have to do something like this to fetch objects rather than arrays from the database</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code> 
protected function _initFetch(){

    $this-&gt;bootstrap('db');
    $db = $this-&gt;getResource('db');

    $db-&gt;setFetchMode(Zend_Db::FETCH_OBJ);

}
</code></pre>

<p>It would be great if the existing Db resource could take another config line like this</p>

<p>resources.db.fetchMode = 5</p>

